<h1 style="color: #2E4AFF; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">Welcome to AlooChat!</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>

<p>Your AlooChat account has been created successfully. Here are your login details:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #2E4AFF; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 16px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></p>
  <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Password:</strong> <code style="background-color: #e9ecef; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; font-family: monospace;"><%= @password %></code></p>
</div>

<p>For security reasons, we recommend changing your password after your first login.</p>

<p style="margin: 24px 0;">
  <a href="<%= @action_url %>" style="color: #2E4AFF; font-weight: 500;">Login to Your Account →</a>
</p>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The AlooChat Team</p> 